{"tid":1392901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非進場一齊收工去散步","createTime":"2019-08-01T01:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T16:53:50.000Z","uid":263365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3aa2a3c56ba7f782b4af78fb52854fd46d389530","tid":1392901,"uid":263365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:50:20.000Z","msg":"可以自發性全黑衫/黃雨褸圍住自己區嘅警署散步。唔需要叫口號，只要全港18區有一定人數同時散步，個畫面一定好震撼。<br />\n冇暴力冇衝突冇佔領，日日散步唔阻人搵食又可以方便和理非。<br />\n<br />\n大家參詳吓睇吓得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真唔想俾政府有理由出水炮車，外國當過兵都攪唔掂，香港嘅年輕人⋯真係唔敢諗。你地已經付出好多，唔可以再白白送頭。<br />\n<br />\n5大訴求<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n萬事小心"},{"pid":"233ea9d39365dcc8d49426c7a42a482eed52aece","tid":1392901,"uid":263365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:50:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4818d189ff6eff56af01f7fe4cfad275c005a565","tid":1392901,"uid":263365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:50:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1e9d92077d2a4b9e45951b280a0d83f3a243c42","tid":1392901,"uid":263365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab263321edfa47b91c3351169953adf1d8e5df2f","tid":1392901,"uid":263365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:51:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd558a00b42376d02f7eb075680dcdf218437665","tid":1392901,"uid":263365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"0a83a2f8f940a779ff53e413d67673475394aae8","tid":1392901,"uid":263365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:53:40.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"e981d02e0478cee73b7f7e6c527c1b0d2591df7f","tid":1392901,"uid":263365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"